"1 tablespoon safflower oil","1  medium yellow onion, finely chopped","2  garlic cloves, minced","1/2 cup water","3 tablespoons cranberry sauce","2 teaspoons adobo sauce","1  small chipotle chile (canned in adobo sauce), chopped","2 cups leftover shredded skinless turkey breast (about 9 ounces)","1 cup cooked brown rice","10  Bibb lettuce leaves","3  julienne-cut radishes","1/3 cup cilantro leaves","1/2 cup tomatillo salsa"